text: Xiangyang Subdistrict () is a subdistrict in Linwei District, Weinan, Shaanxi, China. , it has 26 residential communities under its administration. == See also == * List of township-level divisions of Shaanxi == References == Category:Township-level divisions of Shaanxi Category:Weinan
